## ── PART 9: Why Neural Networks? ───────────────────
##
## Neural networks can learn COMPLEX patterns
## that simple linear regression cannot.
##
## Examples:
##   - Image recognition (cat vs dog)
##   - Language translation
##   - Game playing (chess, Go)
##   - Music generation
##
## The secret: multiple layers let the network
## learn hierarchies of patterns.
##
## ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

print("PART 9: Why Neural Networks?")
print("─────────────────────────────")
print("")

print("Neural networks learn COMPLEX patterns:")
print("  - Image recognition")
print("  - Language translation")
print("  - Game playing")
print("  - Music generation")
print("")
print("Secret: multiple layers learn hierarchies")
print("")

